# feature funnel

- homework tracking system:
  - [x] a dedicated homework group that is linked to main group same as training groups
  - [x] homework gets posted in that group this should be recognised by the bot.
  - [x] students start sending replies this is also recognised as submitting homework by the bot.
  - [x] teachers (new type homework teachers) will reply to students.
  - [x] teachers reply should be tracked as reviewed homework by the bot.
  - for offline mode:
    - [x] enable student role of class management.
    - [x] teacher can add homework in text, photo, and or voice.
    - [x] a user with student role can see/hear homework
    - [x] a user with student role can submit a homework
    - [x] homework can be voice or text or photo.
    - [x] teacher would be able to review homework from offline panel and reply to student.
    - [x] student can see teacher reply and resubmit homework.
    - in case students were not involved in offline mode (some students are not able to handle automated tasks):
      - [x] operator/assistent should be able to create a list of submitted homework and mark reviewed homework, resubmitted homework per student
    - [x] we should be able to print a report of submitted homework and reviewed homework, resubmitted homework.
